data.description: Beautiful well maintained 3bed/ 2.5bath duplex. Spacious kitchen with laundry room downstairs, large living room with fireplace. Outside patio for grilling and backyard activities. All bedrooms are located upstairs with two bathrooms as well. Plenty of space for at home office or home gym. Located close to local restaurants and shopping in the area.
